Installation:

        git clone git://github.com/gabriellima/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

        ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
        ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Download submodules:

        cd ~/.vim
        git submodule init
        git submodule update

Download dependencies of submodules:

            cd ~/.vim/bundle/pyflakes-vim
            git submodule init
            git submodule update
